{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0fff0c3114","title":"周炳生的右派言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ceafd7c503","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"0fff0c3114"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"00d8e3d85b","name":"河南医学院"},{"id":"be63cb0cb4","name":"周炳生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"936b8479fd","type":"title","text":"周炳生的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"e60feddf61","type":"authors","text":"河南医学院周炳生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"77eed99c13","type":"subtitle","text":"[周炳生：河南医学院26期学生]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"3525e11a5d","type":"paragraph","text":"合作化偏激了。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"03f6c863b7","type":"paragraph","text":"农村干部品质恶劣，上拍下压，大干部好办，小干部难缠。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"5fbd8943bb","type":"paragraph","text":"乡村干部是土包子，作风恶劣，他们领导不但不能增产，反而减产。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"6a8430c840","type":"paragraph","text":"党在学校一贯对知识分子和青年残酷、歧视、打击，是在危害革命，已造成恶果。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"fddc7e23c8","type":"paragraph","text":"老师思想改造回来都没劲，给肉也吃不下，共产党就是要把一切人都改造得服从自己。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"a8bc2b473c","type":"paragraph","text":"有些苏联不用的东西，但我们却把它当作先进经验用，为什么我们中国老知识分子的经验抛弃而采用苏联的呢？","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"aae54b293d","type":"paragraph","text":"苏联科学受政治限制，因此我反对社会主义，也就反对苏联科学。李森科太幼稚，米丘林学说不正派，摩尔根学说正派。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"ea4db2cdfc","type":"paragraph","text":"苏联的唯物主义所以战胜唯心主义是因为会议举手表决的结果。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"0875c8ce15","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党只讲阶级斗争，党对啥都拿阶级斗争来说话。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"9dd217ec7e","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党只讲阶级斗争，先是收买穷人，利用穷人斗富人，再利用富人为他们要天下，这真是“口甜心辣，先哄后杀”。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"3c0b4865bf","type":"paragraph","text":"我要是老包刘荣，把人都得三分之二铡。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"8b92863044","type":"paragraph","text":"我要当了法院院长，要狠狠地杀人。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"17cb7884ae","type":"paragraph","text":"提候选人进行选择是不民主的。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"312cd5cea5","type":"paragraph","text":"现在的电影是黄色的，小说唯心的。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"263931c4ea","type":"paragraph","text":"“党天下”在全国有无，我不知道，至少河南医学院是有的，储安平的“党天下”击中了要害，发现了新问题。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"},{"id":"ce89314c83","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《右派言论集》（河南医学院马列主义教研室编印，1958年4月）。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114"}],"page":{"id":"61b186a0de","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0fff0c3114","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}